Quote:  <i>Broad-billed Prion Pachyptila vittata vittata</i> (FORSTER, 1777) ... OTHER NAMES:

<i>Whalebird, scooper, blue-billy, parara. ... Body blue-grey with conspicuous black open-M pattern across upper wings. </i>
